CITENOTE = Please acknowledge the <a href="https://elrc-share.eu/repository/browse/english-slovak-corpus-of-annual-reports-from-the-slovak-national-centre-for-human-rights-website-processed/bbb12696031a11e9b7d400155d0267064d22b1247dc94beca0915584845b594f/">original sources and providers</a> of the data and also <a href="http://opus.lingfil.uu.se/LREC2012.txt">cite the following article</a> if you use the OPUS packages and downloads in your own work:<br/> J. Tiedemann, 2012, <a href="http://www.lrec-conf.org/proceedings/lrec2012/pdf/463_Paper.pdf"><i>Parallel Data, Tools and Interfaces in OPUS.</i></a> In Proceedings of the 8th International Conference on Language Resources and Evaluation (LREC 2012)
